  abstract={Introduction: 
Treatment of fractures and dislocations of the thoracolumbar spine is aimed at achieving a stable and painless spine. Concerning mode of treatment therapists are divided into two groups--those for conservative approach and those who advocate operative stabilization of spinal column. The objective of this paper was to compare radiological findings of both modes of treatment on the basis of our clinical material.
