  keywords={Radiculopathy, Cementation, Spine, Kyphoplasty, Spinal Cord Diseases, Vertebroplasty, Spinal Fractures, Retrospective Studies, Postoperative Complications, Osteoporosis, Middle Aged, Male, Humans, Female, Factor Analysis, Statistical, Extravasation of Diagnostic and Therapeutic Materials, Bone Cements, Aged, 80 and over, Aged},
  abstract={Objective: 
To explore the correlative factors affecting the complications resulting from cement leakage after percutaneous kyphoplasty (PKP) in the treatment of osteoporotic vertebral body compression fractures (OVCF).
Methods: 
